flowchart TD
    subgraph Discovery
        A[Idea / Bug / Feature] --> B{Existe REQ?}
        B -->|No| C[Crear REQ-XX-slug\nopenspec/changes/]
        B -->|Sí| D[Abrir REQ existente]
        C --> E[Definir req.md + state.yaml\nstatus: active]
        D --> F[Identificar HU faltante]
    end

    subgraph SDD["SDD First"]
        F --> G{Existe HU?}
        G -->|No| H[HU-Y.Z-slug/\nhu.md + proposal.md]
        H --> I[design.md + tasks.md]
        I --> J[state.yaml → proposed]
        G -->|Sí| K[state.yaml → in_progress]
        J --> K
    end

    subgraph Implementacion["Implementación (TDD)"]
        K --> L[RED: escribir test que falla]
        L --> M[GREEN: mínimo para que pase]
        M --> N[REFACTOR: mejorar sin romper]
        N --> O[SABOTAJE: romper fix]
        O --> P{Test cae?}
        P -->|Sí| Q[Restaurar fix]
        P -->|No| R[Arreglar test primero]
        R --> L
        Q --> S[go test ./... ✅]
    end

    subgraph Cierre
        S --> T[state.yaml → implemented]
        T --> U[git commit]
        U --> V{todo el REQ\nimplementado?}
        V -->|No| F
        V -->|Sí| W[state.yaml REQ → archived]
    end

    W --> X[Fin 🎯]
